Interface INavigator

Provides ways to Navigate between components and get notified when a NavigatorComponent recieves a new component to navigate to

Namespace: Onbox.Mvc.V7
Assembly: Onbox.Mvc.V7.dll

Attach<TParent, TNavComponent>(TParent, TNavComponent)

Hooks up a NavigatorComponent and its parent to the Navigation System. It will automatically be notified of navigation changes and control its life cycle and cleaning up after unloading.

Subscribe<TParent>(Action<IMvcComponent>)

Gets notified when the default NavigatorComponent (x:Name == 'Navigator') of a specific Parent changes. Remember to call Unsubscribe to avoid memory leaks.
